    <item>
      <title>美国国债下跌，避险买盘减弱，焦点转向拍卖</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/us-treasuries-fall-as-haven-bid-fades-traders-focus-on-auction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于全球对避险资产的需求减弱，美国国债价格下跌，市场目前转向 580 亿美元的拍卖，作为对投资者兴趣的下一个考验。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/us-treasuries-fall-as-haven-bid-fades-traders-focus-on-auction</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 08:06:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
